QuestData.Title: Uruk!
QuestData.Description: Uruk is the Deadtalker of the Townlong yaungol. Your mission will not be truly complete until you defeat him. Go to it!
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: The corrupted Deadtalker of the Townlong yaungol.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill Uruk at Deadtalker's Plateau in Townlong Steppes.
